# About

Hello! I'm Lautaro Acosta Quintana, a programmer from Argentina. I'm currently pursuing an Information Systems Engineering degree at [UTN](https://www.frre.utn.edu.ar/). You can find my résumé in [English](https://cdn.lautaroacosta.com/resume_us_3.pdf) or [Spanish](https://cdn.lautaroacosta.com/resume_es_3.pdf).

I love to code and I'm focused on doing work that has real impact on people's lives.

All my life I couldn't help but [ask questions](https://jvns.ca/blog/good-questions/), so I've decided to write about the things I find that are interesting.
